Hmm, a letter for Snoopy.
I never get letters.

21:40.925 --> 21:43.260
Nobody ever writes to me.

21:43.427 --> 21:48.349
I had 14 pen pals once,
but I did all the writing.

21:49.767 --> 21:52.478
Here, Snoopy. You got a letter.

21:57.691 --> 21:59.902
[YAWNS]

22:34.770 --> 22:35.813
[SNAPPING]

22:36.897 --> 22:39.900
[FINGERS SNAPPING]

22:43.279 --> 22:44.321
[THUDDING]

22:52.621 --> 22:55.958
What's going on?
Why are you packed?

22:57.209 --> 23:01.130
Are you going someplace?
What's going on?

23:02.590 --> 23:04.466
Where is he going?

23:05.175 --> 23:07.428
I never know what's going on.

23:57.853 --> 23:59.104
[GRUNTS]

24:52.366 --> 24:54.368
[THUNDER CLAPPING]

25:13.429 --> 25:14.847
He's gone.

25:15.014 --> 25:16.640
[SCHROEDER PLAYING PIANO]

25:19.601 --> 25:21.812
I don't understand it.

25:21.979 --> 25:23.689
Who is Lila?

25:23.856 --> 25:27.526
You say he got this letter
and then he just took off?

25:27.693 --> 25:29.903
Well, what does the letter say,
Charlie Brown?

25:30.654 --> 25:35.409
"Dear Snoopy, I have been
in the hospital for three weeks,

25:35.784 --> 25:37.536
and I am very lonely.

25:37.703 --> 25:40.581
Could you come to see me?
Love, Lila."

25:40.748 --> 25:43.625
Lila? Who in the world is Lila?

25:43.792 --> 25:48.380
If I don't find out who Lila is,
I'll go crazy.

26:25.918 --> 26:27.753
[CAR VROOMS]

27:32.151 --> 27:34.153
[GIBBERING]

27:53.714 --> 27:56.133
I don't understand it.

27:56.300 --> 27:58.552
Why would Snoopy go to Lila?

27:58.719 --> 28:01.513
Maybe Snoopy felt
he needed a vacation.

28:01.680 --> 28:04.766
Maybe his life with you
was getting too boring.

28:04.933 --> 28:07.436
Boring? What was I supposed to do?

28:07.603 --> 28:10.439
- Keep him entertained?
- I don't know.

28:10.606 --> 28:13.192
What do other dog owners do?

28:13.358 --> 28:16.403
I never thought of myself
as being a dog owner.

28:16.570 --> 28:18.989
Snoopy was more like a friend.

28:19.156 --> 28:21.992
Friends get bored too,
Charlie Brown.

28:23.160 --> 28:24.494
[SIGHS]

29:21.260 --> 29:24.471
- Hey, Ma, I've found a stray dog.
SNOOPY: Aah!

29:24.638 --> 29:26.640
Ma, oh, Ma.

29:29.142 --> 29:30.644
[GULPS]

29:35.148 --> 29:36.942
[GRUNTING]

29:45.826 --> 29:48.662
Oh, boy, I found a lost bird.

29:50.330 --> 29:54.376
Hey, Ma, I found a lost bird! Ma!

29:55.127 --> 29:57.045
I got a bird, Ma.

29:57.629 --> 30:01.633
To add to my collection, Ma.
A dog and a bird.

30:03.135 --> 30:04.469
[SIGHS]

30:05.178 --> 30:07.514
This is great. I have two pets.

30:07.681 --> 30:10.517
Hey, Ma, I got two pets!

30:10.684 --> 30:12.311
A Sheepdog and a parrot.

30:12.477 --> 30:14.479
Hey, Ma. Can I keep them, Ma?

30:15.355 --> 30:16.648
[SIGHS]

30:17.733 --> 30:20.861
Hi, puppy. Mom says I can keep you.

30:21.028 --> 30:23.780
Boy, I always wanted a dog.

30:24.239 --> 30:26.616
I think I‘ll give you a good dog name.

30:28.160 --> 30:29.619
Rex?

30:30.203 --> 30:32.164
Hey, how about Rex?

30:32.748 --> 30:33.832
[GROANS]

30:33.999 --> 30:35.959
Here, Rex! Here, Rex! Here!

30:36.126 --> 30:37.377
[MAKES KISSING NOISES]

30:37.544 --> 30:42.591
