01:16:44.266 --> 01:16:45.893
- He's back.
- He's back.

01:16:46.060 --> 01:16:47.770
- He's back.
- He's back.

01:16:47.937 --> 01:16:51.524
[SINGING] <i>Harmony is where it’s at</i>

01:16:51.690 --> 01:16:55.152
<i>And where it’s at for you
Is where it’s at for us</i>

01:16:55.319 --> 01:16:58.948
<i>Share and share alike
Is what it’s all about</i>

01:16:59.115 --> 01:17:02.868
<i>And what it’s all about
Just makes it right to us</i>

01:17:03.035 --> 01:17:06.413
<i>Partners, pals!
Comrades, chums!</i>

01:17:06.580 --> 01:17:09.542
<i>Buddies to the end whatever comes</i>

01:17:10.376 --> 01:17:13.420
<i>Me and you, a happy crew</i>

01:17:13.587 --> 01:17:17.675
<i>Side by side we’re uniﬁed
And we will never be divided</i>

01:17:17.842 --> 01:17:21.303
<i>Lose or win, sink or swim</i>

01:17:21.470 --> 01:17:25.141
<i>We’re the best of buddies, Snoopy
We’re the best of buddies</i>

01:17:25.307 --> 01:17:30.688
<i>We ‚re the best of buddies
Me and you</i>

01:17:37.528 --> 01:17:39.155
[SNAPPING]

01:18:14.732 --> 01:18:17.109
Look at this, Charlie Brown.

01:18:19.236 --> 01:18:24.283
"To Linus Van Pelt,
I expect my croquet set and chess set

01:18:24.450 --> 01:18:28.370
returned forthwith in good order
and within five days,

01:18:28.537 --> 01:18:30.831
or the matter will be turned over
to my attorney."

01:18:31.457 --> 01:18:35.336
And mine says, he wants
the record collection back.

01:18:35.920 --> 01:18:40.382
Mine says that since he gave me
nothing, I owe him nothing.

01:18:40.549 --> 01:18:42.676
That does it, Charlie Brown!

01:18:42.843 --> 01:18:45.804
He's your dog
and you're welcome to him.

